{"id":14881758,"mediaExerciseId":"0360b13b-7871-4529-9d26-2920161370f6","exerciseName":"7","chapterName":"21","chapterTitle":"International Corporate Finance","groupId":null,"groupTitle":null,"isPremium":true,"sectionName":"21.7","sectionTitle":"Political Risk","pageNumber":732,"solutions":[{"id":5977639,"modifiedOn":"2021-01-01T00:00:00.000000","steps":[{"columns":[{"text":"In this exercise, we are asked to explain the concepts of political risk.","images":{"latex":{"large":{"height":28,"srcUrl":"https://d2nchlq0f2u6vy.cloudfront.net/22/01/02/62bd447a6493ab39d2f246469c0ecce1/7d0ceb66fee41b520ac07b652b985118/lateximg_large.png","width":919},"regular":{"height":15,"srcUrl":"https://d2nchlq0f2u6vy.cloudfront.net/22/01/02/62bd447a6493ab39d2f246469c0ecce1/7d0ceb66fee41b520ac07b652b985118/lateximg.png","width":459}},"additional":null},"hasInvalidKatex":false,"isTextOnly":true}],"isResult":false,"stepNumber":1},{"columns":[{"text":"## 7a.\n\nWe are asked to define a political risk.","images":{"latex":null,"additional":null},"hasInvalidKatex":false,"isTextOnly":false}],"isResult":false,"stepNumber":2},{"columns":[{"text":"A **political risk** is a risk related to changes in value because of *political actions*. Some countries have a higher political risk than others. The higher the political risk, the higher required return on overseas investments. Moreover, political risk also depends on the nature of the business since the more valuable the business is, the higher its political risk. ","images":{"latex":{"large":{"height":181,"srcUrl":"https://d2nchlq0f2u6vy.cloudfront.net/22/01/02/62bd447a6493ab39d2f246469c0ecce1/f1d3f0e345388895d0b5eeae44bfe6e2/lateximg_large.png","width":997},"regular":{"height":91,"srcUrl":"https://d2nchlq0f2u6vy.cloudfront.net/22/01/02/62bd447a6493ab39d2f246469c0ecce1/f1d3f0e345388895d0b5eeae44bfe6e2/lateximg.png","width":498}},"additional":null},"hasInvalidKatex":false,"isTextOnly":false}],"isResult":false,"stepNumber":3},{"columns":[{"text":"## 7b.\n\nWe are asked to identify ways of hedging political risk.","images":{"latex":null,"additional":null},"hasInvalidKatex":false,"isTextOnly":false}],"isResult":false,"stepNumber":4},{"columns":[{"text":"Political risk can be hedged in various ways. First is the **use of local financing from government of foreign country** as this reduces the political risk since the company has an option to refuse to pay because of unfavorable political activities. Another way is the **structuring of the operation** wherein a parent company is required to be involve to reduce the political risk. Lastly is to operate in a **country with lesser risk** as less risky country reduces political risk as well.","images":{"latex":{"large":{"height":256,"srcUrl":"https://d2nchlq0f2u6vy.cloudfront.net/22/01/02/62bd447a6493ab39d2f246469c0ecce1/689691903a6ef050ec3e0f2636d07f58/lateximg_large.png","width":997},"regular":{"height":128,"srcUrl":"https://d2nchlq0f2u6vy.cloudfront.net/22/01/02/62bd447a6493ab39d2f246469c0ecce1/689691903a6ef050ec3e0f2636d07f58/lateximg.png","width":498}},"additional":null},"hasInvalidKatex":false,"isTextOnly":false}],"isResult":false,"stepNumber":5},{"columns":[{"text":"As a conclusion, we have explained the concepts of political risk.","images":{"latex":{"large":{"height":28,"srcUrl":"https://d2nchlq0f2u6vy.cloudfront.net/22/01/02/62bd447a6493ab39d2f246469c0ecce1/585425c649cb576af4ac312b9b3c1994/lateximg_large.png","width":856},"regular":{"height":15,"srcUrl":"https://d2nchlq0f2u6vy.cloudfront.net/22/01/02/62bd447a6493ab39d2f246469c0ecce1/585425c649cb576af4ac312b9b3c1994/lateximg.png","width":428}},"additional":null},"hasInvalidKatex":false,"isTextOnly":true}],"isResult":false,"stepNumber":6}],"rating":5,"solutionUuid":"4d56d780-53ff-436f-987d-314fca8698e3","editorVersion":2,"answeredOn":null,"ratingCount":null,"solutionOrder":null,"totalSteps":6}],"textbook":{"authors":"Bradford D. Jordan, Randolph W. Westerfield, Stephen A. Ross","imageUrl":"https://d2nchlq0f2u6vy.